    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057290/extras/c257de7ea95486eee378b7a900343efd.poster.avif?t=1763224263\" width=616 height=50 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057290/extras/c257de7ea95486eee378b7a900343efd.webm?t=1763224263\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057290/extras/c257de7ea95486eee378b7a900343efd.mp4?t=1763224263\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057290/extras/8057fdbba2ad081f80830cd59115c4db.poster.avif?t=1763224263\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057290/extras/8057fdbba2ad081f80830cd59115c4db.webm?t=1763224263\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057290/extras/8057fdbba2ad081f80830cd59115c4db.mp4?t=1763224263\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>踏上与勇敢的 Indica MacJones 一起寻找传说中的圣杯的神秘而轻松的冒险之旅。在旅途中，你会遇到迷人的 furry 同伴，解开古老的谜题，并探索隐藏的神秘地点，在那里等待着未被发现的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057290/extras/87a07bcea14f31373f7533f524d694c3.avif?t=1763224263\" width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为这次探险的领袖，你需要研究古老的地图，管理资源，并派遣团队去探索未知的土地。每一个决定都可能让你更接近圣杯的发现——但要做好面对意想不到的挑战和惊喜的准备。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >受经典冒险电影最佳传统的启发，<strong>Furry Adventure Club and the Holy Grail 🦁</strong> 带来了探索和解谜的乐趣，一同追寻历史上最伟大的传奇之一。准备好加入冒险了吗？<strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong></p>",
